## Conversation Messages [/api/v1/conversazioni/{id}/messaggi]

+ Parameters
    + id: `6825bf2d4b0d6f001234fa01` (string, required)

### Get messages [GET]

+ Request
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer jwt-token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "ok": true,
          "data": {
            "messaggi": [
              {
                "_id": "6825bf6f4b0d6f001234fa11",
