+ Parameters
    + costoMax: `20` (number, optional) - Filtra coupon con costoCrediti <= costoMax
    + page: `1` (number, optional)
    + limit: `20` (number, optional)

+ Request
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer jwt-token

